@node 25 "Controls and options."

                               @{u}Control of the ghost @{uu}

     The @{b}mouse@{ub} is used to move the ghost.              .

     The @{b}left button@{ub} is used to make the ghost turn around toward the left side.

     The @{b}right button@{ub} is used to make the ghost turn around toward the right side.

     @{b}P@{ub} enables (or disables) the pause mode..

     @{b}ESC@{ub} is used to quit ( we mean abandon) the current game and return back to the
main menu..

                                @{u} The main menu @{uu}

     @{b}LIVES@{ub}                    3,5 or 7: it stands for the difficulty rate of the game.

     @{b}AUDIO MODE@{ub}   @{fg shine}MUSIC@{fg text}        <- Music on 3 voices, sounds on 1.
                  @{fg shine}SFX@{fg text}          <- Sounds on 4 voices.
                  @{fg shine}SILENCE@{fg text}      <- The noise of silence on four voices.


     @{b}INTERLACED@{ub}                Enables or disables the interlaced screen.

     @{b}VIDEO MODE@{ub}   @{fg shine}NORMAL@{fg text}       Classical appearance of the screen.
                  @{fg shine}OLD MOVIE@{fg text}    You play in black and white like in the old movie. Rather excellent no ?
                  @{fg shine}GAMEBOY@{fg text}      Bubble on a japenese product.

     @{b}RESET HIGHSCORES@{ub}          Clear the highscores table: the names are the default ones.

     @{b}PASSWORD@{ub}                  To restart in the room where you lost your last life
     (in the condition this room has a odd number) with the number of lives you had when you
     entered this level..It resets your score.

     @{b}START GAME@{ub}                To begin a new game.


                              @{u}Others informations@{uu}

  When you are on the title screens, press ESC to come back to the Workbench screen.

  In game you get a new life every 30000 points.Don't hestitate to activate handles or buttons.
  Collect new lives or fruit bonuses with the bubble.

  If you make a new highscore, you can record it on disk by pressing "y" when it is requested

  When you die, codes are given to you in the gameover page. There are three codes which appear one
after the other and warp until you press the mouse left button. They are used to access the last
odd levels.


@endnode

